						 <p>Anderson Skip.</p> <p>I suppose this could be considered an epilogue of sorts to the Anderson Robotics storyline, which got so wrapped up in the human characters at times it neglected that the robots were beings themselves, many of which were sapient. And now they are pissed&#8230;</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053795" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" >Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053795" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" >GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053795" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" >Randomini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2826145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053795" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2826145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" >Tufto</a></span>,<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/subtletea" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?user